Content: The Gaming place is a group where all non-competitive and competitive can play relax and have with others. We have an application that will be sent if you are interested. We participate in regular play and have tournaments where you earn money_ we also hold training sessions for the newbies or amateurs trying to learn we also hold a competition every Friday to see who is the best on the server. We accept all platforms and accept ages 12+. We are all about fun so Join! ( We are new)
